title: PBE SIGN UP HELP

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: Hey guys i cant sign in pbe i really want account to play :(((( but i cant fix this https://gyazo.com/f20efb964da1af858d721dc437a1b81f pls help me im playing on EUNE

replies.body:
It looks like you're having issues because you're trying to access the NA link. Try [**clearing your browser's cache**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies), then login to your account from the [**EUNE Homepage**](http://eune.leagueoflegends.com/), finally, you can visit the [**EUNE PBE Signup Page**](https://pbesignup.eune.leagueoflegends.com/en/pbe).

Let me know if this worked for you. :)
